page.title: 01IN THE NEW FOREST
page.content: The forest in {BEAULIEU}has many trees and it has some swamps.The swamps are in the low land and there are a lot by Gurnet Fields next to NORTH GATE. } There is a small car park and there are some EVERGREEN trees and a few DECIDUOUS trees.The forest has many large areas without trees and it has some small areas with some scrub land. The{NORTH GATE}area has a lot of flat land with no trees and it is used by {scouts}to walk past a lot of trees and scrub land.The scrub land is by { {PENERLY LODGE}and it has a huge hill and lot of inclosures,the hill is 40 feet tall and it rises very fast. { }
